**Job Description**:

- Join the founding team and work with a group of passionate and talented engineers to create the new SSE (Security Service Edge) product. We utilize all the latest technologies to ensure its scalability and usability;
- Responsible for planning, designing and building front-end technology solutions;
- Responsible for the overall control and coordination of the front-end product to ensure excellent user experience

Job Requirement:

- Bachelor degree or above, at leaset 3 years front-end R&D experience
- In-depth understanding of mainstream architecture such as **react, vue, **can independently develop **common components **, familiar with **react, nodejs, webpack **is preferred;
- Familiar with **w3c **standards, have a deeper understanding of front-end modular development, and be able to produce high-quality design and code;
- Have a unique understanding of **UI visual **interaction and front-end data presentation, able to build products with strong usability and smooth experience;
- Passionate, with excellent learning ability, strong sense of responsibility and mission, good communication and collaboration skills.

Bonus Points
- Strong cross-platform development experience, mobile/client side
- Proficient in **golang, python, nodejs **and can be used for daily development.
- Good documentation skills
